data.description: Restored classic 1926 Alameda bungalow with modern upgrades.  Amazing floor plan with main level living. Four bedrooms - two bedrooms on main level, and two spacious true primary suites; one with balcony overlooking backyard. Many classic period details throughout home including hardwoods, bathroom tile, clawfoot tub, and built-in charm. Enjoy the backyard with covered outdoor living + built-in bar, Grilling shed, tool shed or chicken coop, detached garage, fenced in yard, and raised garden beds. Home has been updated with newer windows, systems and newer furnace. Prime location blocks to Alberta Arts, dining, shops, bars, schools, parks and all your essential needs.OPEN SUNDAY 12/17 2-4pm
